"but first... - Shut the Fuck up!!!"

There’s no question that by now you have an opinion on the song #Selfie. It’s been played so much since its release, even The Chainsmokers were ready to put an end to it.  So the guys approached us to put a unique twist on the track, and we thought it was time for this selfie girl to ‘Shut the fuck up’.
